 2019-04882019-05-09,  AAFC,  ,  , 
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgreement with British-Columbia in order to assist financially agricultural producers
PrecisOrder Authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to ENTER INTO AN AGREEMENT with BRITISH-COLUMBIA and provide up to $600,000 in federal contributions to assist agricultural producers with the extraordinary costs to mitigate, or to recover from the adverse effects of 2018 bovine tuberculosis outbreak in British-Columbia.
